    dc:description "Figure 106 Temnothorax casanovai sp. nov. (A–C) Holotype worker (LACMENT323462). (A) Full-face view. (B) Profile view. (C) Dorsal view. (D–F) Paratype gyne (LACMENT323464). (D) Full-face view. (E) Profile view. (F) Dorsal view. (G) Geographical and elevational distribution of specimens examined. Type localities are represented by triangles, non-type localities are represented by circles. Bounding box in inset map shows location of main map. Scale bars 0.2 mm. Full-size DOI: 10.7717/peerj.11514/fig-106" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5102307/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

